	COMMAND LISTING:

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Command:	WEATHER [<zip>]
Description:	Retrieves weather information
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Command:	DICT <string>
Description:	Looks up string in dictionary and refers URL
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Command:	HOST <dns>
Description:	Uses the unix program host to lookup a dns
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Command:	THES <string>
Description:	Find words related to a string
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Command:	XLATE <lang> <string>
Description:	Translates a string using the language perameter
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Command:	RQUOTE 
Description:	Display random quote
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Command:	SERVERLIST
Description:	Display Server List
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Command:	NICKLIST
Description:	Display Nickname list
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Command:	CHANLIST
Description:	Display Channel list
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Command:	VERISON
Description:	Display version information
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Command:	SENTENCE
Description:	Outputs random sentence
Requirements:	sentence.c must be compiled (done in defualt setup)
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Command:	STATS
Description:	Display stats
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Command:	UPTIME
Description:	Display bot's uptime
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Command:	SYSUPTIME
Description:	Display the uptime of the bot's host system
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Command:	SYSINFO
Description:	Display information about the bot's host system
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Command:	SLASHDOT
Description:	Display slashdot headlines
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Command:	FRESHMEAT
Description:	Display freshmeat headlines
